title: Prince Harry and fiancee Meghan visit Invictus Games trials
text:
Prince Harry and fiancee Meghan visit Invictus Games trials 2:48pm BST - 00:49 
Prince Harry and Meghan Markle cheer on competitors hoping to be chosen to represent the UK in the Invictus Games later this year. Rough cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
